original_title: Trace Adkins: Live from Austin TX
overview: Performing music from his "Dreamin' Out Loud" and "Big Time" albums, multiple gold- and platinum-selling country music singer Trace Adkins excites a Texas crowd with his rich baritone in this 1997 concert recorded live for "Austin City Limits." Songs include "(This Ain't) No Thinkin' Thing," "If I Fall," "There's a Girl in Texas," "The Rest of Mine," "Lonely Won't Leave Me Alone" and "Big Time," plus eight more fan favorites.
title: Trace Adkins: Live from Austin TX
